text: Baba Mungipa Law College is in Pilani, Rajasthan, India, is affiliated to the University of Rajasthan, Jaipur, which was established in 1988. It is approved by Bar Council of India. ==References== Category:Law schools in Rajasthan Category:Jhunjhunu district Category:Educational institutions established in 1998 Category:1988 establishments in India
